# Object Detection API installation

This guide is superseded by the root README.

From an activated tf2-object-detection Conda environment, run:

    powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File scripts/setup_object_detection.ps1

The script clones the current TensorFlow Model Garden locally, compiles Protobuf definitions, installs Object Detection API into the active environment, and runs the official verification test. It does not copy protoc.exe to system directories or set a global PYTHONPATH.
